'desc': [u'

Sleep Dry Baby Care Sheet Medium Bedsheet Price: Rs.265

The maroon Sleep Dry Baby Care Sheet is visually appealing and will help you in keeping your infant’s bed dry as they are waterproof. These Baby Sheets are dried easily and the sweat breathable aspect of these sheets will keep your tiny tot’s skin fresh and free of skin irritations. As dust mites are repelled by this Sleep Dry Sheet you can be sure that your infant will stay safe from insects and insect bites. The anti-bacterial and anti-microbial characteristic of the Sleep Dry Baby Care Sheets make them absolutely safe and apt for use in an infant’s cot or cradle.

The anti-slip feature will make sure that the sheet remains in its place even if your tiny tot manages to move a lot in the cot. With a light weight and dimensions of 1 x .7 m this Baby Care Sheet from Sleep Dry is easy-to-use. The warm and soft feel of the fabric will ensure that your bundle of joy enjoys a peaceful and relaxing sleep. When grimed
column15:
these Sleep Dry Baby Care Sheets can be easily cleaned by simply washing them with hand. The stain-relief feature will ensure that the visual appeal of these Maroon Sheets does not get faded out.
